He said courses are offered for children, from the age of 12 and adults.
What you should keep in your First Aid kit:


 Gloves
 Bandages/gauze
 Splinter
 Savlon
 Plasters
 Tweezers
 Safety pins
 Antiseptic cream


Medicines should be checked regularly to make sure they're within their use-by dates.

